'''Beambaiting''' was a tactic used by the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]]. A small naval unit, often a [[Line of battle#Galactic Empire|Pursuit Line]], would chase a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] unit to a world known to harbor Rebel sympathizers, who would launch reinforcements. The Imperials would stage a retreat, followed by the larger Rebel fleet, to a point where a prearranged Imperial attack group would emerge from [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] and obliterate the Rebels.

